{"tid":1430653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武暫時休息兩三日，請和理手足千萬不要做下一波五感精神攻勢：視聽嗅味觸","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:06:34.000Z","uid":35776,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0086c7437cf2cdfb0673f4944287a57daf2905","tid":1430653,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:53:28.000Z","msg":"視聽嗅味觸<br />\n以下係錯誤信息，千祈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">視</span></strong></span>：<br />\n正在進行或做過嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>社區廣播系列</strong></span> &mdash; 黑社會同狗嘅暴行記錄，連儂牆，長輩圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>思想改造系列</strong></span> &mdash; 對狗不斷灌輸<strong>大媽</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />片，耳濡目染<strong>公狗母狗可能改變性僻愛上大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，</strong>無法再對細路女出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大媽歌舞系列：魔音貫腦嘅大媽歌，民族歌，吹Dee打<br />\n口號系列：要光復香港 時代革命 (林鄭月娥, 2019) 黑社會 社會垃圾等<br />\n千祈唔好對狗屋或半夜三更對住狗竇播放，住越高層聽得越遠，局住聽晒聽到有陰影<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嗅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n臭蛋之外，最直接係用腐爛有機物質發酵<br />\n，聚集一堆係狗屋隔離行過，腐爛物質浸水都係樣效果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">味</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n凍撚水 屙華田 白汁 蛋白 不必多解釋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n施加身上所有：油 波子 不一足矣<br />\n<br />\n以上描述行為千祈唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c550b5caf722784165284f468fb8b7832cbcac1a","tid":1430653,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:59:25.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n最憎人樓下嘈鳩住我"},{"pid":"b749c18c4264f6e932ad350d8129cbd7f11ca282","tid":1430653,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:00:59.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳] FORWARDED FROM TELEGRAM<br />\n朋友既朋友 警隊臨床心理學家指出唔少警察<br />\n長期聽到針對警察示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱、最嚴重會患上抑鬱等<br />\n<br />\n若示威者同警察距離非常近既時候, 利用群眾優勢<br />\n不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」,這種標籤化令警察內心會感自愧, 壓力倍僧, 行為自動檢點<br />\n<br />\n進一步造成心理創傷口號，不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n試著說<span style=\"color: red;\">「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」</span>此口號出自警察誓言, 當有人不斷叫出此口號，警察會回憶畢業既誓言，開始對自己身份認同產生懷疑同混淆, 精神疲乏, 有部份警察雙眼通紅、帶有淚光<br />\n<br />\n終極核彈級口號, 有機會造成永久心理創傷, 相信好快用得「殺人兇手」 當事實真的發生，不論兇手有沒有殺人，身處同一個群體，都變成兇手, <br />\n不單面對極大壓力而崩塌, 伴隨的是恐懼、抑鬱, 更重要是這種負面情緒會災難性地爆發傳遍整個群體"},{"pid":"463bcedcb9a483f543c672ec6321981901837f72","tid":1430653,"uid":83446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:02:01.000Z","msg":"視嗰點⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4a6b20499981c34df4fd3ea80bae0b7f95270c","tid":1430653,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"463bcedcb9a483f543c672ec6321981901837f72","tid":1430653,"uid":83446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:02:01.000Z","msg":"視嗰點⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:11:56.000Z","msg":"大媽大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小蝶 娜娜 呀月蛾"},{"pid":"5aa880909a667949cbf967e3653ae3a7c408664e","tid":1430653,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:18:15.000Z","msg":"不畏懼  但你犯緊罪<br />\n不徇私  但你冇良知<br />\n不對他人懷惡意<br />\n一日濫權百幾次"},{"pid":"b7215f46425213e044e15f8ae7c89c444dcda6a6","tid":1430653,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:29:04.000Z","msg":"態度正確 輪流做"},{"pid":"f328470fcc80c072e5e1eaf0ddeb133fcff2bced","tid":1430653,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}